::DrillBit::

"Be right back." He says to KitKat, and the other bots, as he runs after
Terrorsaur. He catches up, outside.
"Hey. You're not going to tell Megatron, are you? Let KitKat try.
She will not be able to succeed. Maybe it will get all this nonesense
out of her head." He started to walk back to the room, and thought.
He new very well that KitKat could do it. She had a the heart of a
soldier, and a leader. Plus, this attack served his own plans.
He walked back into the room.
